title: FromBACnetDevObjPropReference (Function)
text:
FUNCTION FromBACnetDevObjPropReference :
BACnetDevObjPropReference
Returns a BACnetDevObjPropReference struct corresponding to the given IEC_BACNET_DEV_OBJ_PROP_REFERENCE.

rows.Name: bacRef
rows.Comment:
The BACnet device object property reference to convert to a
BACnetDevObjPropReference.
